* [[David L. Gunn]] (2002&ndash;2005)<ref name="pr-gunnfired" /><ref name="nyt-wald1">{{cite news | first = Matthew L. | last = Wald | title = A New York Transit Rescuer Is Hired to Revive Amtrak | url = http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9C0CE7DA103EF934A15757C0A9649C8B63&sec=&spon=&partner=permalink&exprod=permalink | work = New York Times | location = [[New York City|New York, New York]] | date = 2002-04-27 | accessdate = 2008-06-12 }}</ref>
