Amtrak's Board of Directors consists of the following people (updated July 2010):<ref>{{citeweb|title=New board members recognize Amtrak is key to future of passenger rail|date=2010-06-29|url=http://www.rtands.com/newsflash/new-board-members-recognize-amtrak-is-key-to-future-of-passenger-rail.html|accessdate=2010-07-16}}</ref>
